text: Torsten Eriksson (20 February 1891 - 29 July 1979) was a Swedish diver. He competed in the men's plain high diving event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1891 births Category:1979 deaths Category:Swedish male divers Category:Olympic divers of Sweden Category:Divers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Örebro
